				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/A-Ph%C3%B2ng-cung-ph%C3%BA/poem-PRU_ew2Q9_CUGXM-oZrryg">A Phòng cung phú - 阿房宮賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/C%E1%BB%ADu-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-O-sBf9uoQUMb2zDArsEBqw">Cửu nhật - 九日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/%C4%90%C4%83ng-cao-kh%C3%A2u-nhi-v%E1%BB%8Dng-vi%E1%BB%85n-h%E1%BA%A3i/poem-y62SqVjVIDt7kK9fptnSyg">Đăng cao khâu nhi vọng viễn hải - 登高丘而望遠海</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/H%E1%BA%A3i-man-man/poem-lHFJOPQ2RFKE9_tLpjz9eg">Hải man man - 海漫漫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C6%B0-Trinh/Kim-D%E1%BB%B1-lan-%C4%91%C3%A0o/poem-MSCD2FdREHsH_gI7coWlWA">Kim Dự lan đào - 金嶼攔濤</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C6%B0-Trinh/author-t4xvjEQCpJQuGs7GtUeU9A">Nguyễn Cư Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-T%E1%BB%AD-Trinh/%C3%94n-Tuy%E1%BB%81n/poem-lNLaJ0s5sTt5nM7hwUDrTQ">Ôn Tuyền - 溫泉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-T%E1%BB%AD-Trinh/author-IiZgh8rDkgLGPpjj6tgPjQ">Tống Tử Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Ph%C3%B9-dung-n%E1%BB%AF-nhi-lu%E1%BB%B5/poem-R9STBdCyvV6_VYrjugG5yQ">Phù dung nữ nhi luỵ - 芙蓉女兒誄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-th%C3%B9-L%C6%B0-c%E1%BA%A5p-s%E1%BB%B1-V%C3%A2n-Phu-t%E1%BB%A9-huynh-Kh%C3%BAc-giang-h%C3%A0-hoa-h%C3%A0nh-ki%E1%BA%BFn-k%C3%BD-t%E1%BB%8Bnh-tr%C3%ACnh-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-Ti%E1%BB%81n-th%E1%BA%A5t/poem-y4Ue00m6iXhCoiiv_dyZNA">Phụng thù Lư cấp sự Vân Phu tứ huynh “Khúc giang hà hoa hành” kiến ký tịnh trình thướng Tiền thất huynh các lão, Trương thập bát trợ giáo - 奉酬盧給事雲夫四兄曲江苛花行見寄並呈上錢七兄閣老張十八助教</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Ti%E1%BB%83u-nhung-2/poem-jTqcLTBbhkiyo_WCvaEQUQ">Tiểu nhung 2 - 小戎 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%B1-kinh-ph%C3%B3-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-Ti%C3%AAn-huy%E1%BB%87n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C5%A9-b%C3%A1ch-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-qHlDll4qtUH2nCJy2-kR4Q">Tự kinh phó Phụng Tiên huyện vịnh hoài ngũ bách tự - 自京赴奉先縣詠懷五百字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
